{"tid":862941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林忌: 連登仔信哂親中媒體「線報」既報導, 炒哂車","createTime":"2018-10-15T08:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T12:51:17.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9f2247d4872433676d91ee8d8890784b087c26d4","tid":862941,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T08:54:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10155566314876121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguy%2Fposts%2F10155566314876121&d=jYrhfx%2BEK%2F53d5JphhnXyv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c4bd8629\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/fokguy/posts/10155566314876121</a><br />\n<br />\nKay Lam<br />\n11分鐘 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n求證了昨日劉小麗在遊行時，被支持填海的大媽鬧癡線，佢反駁「返大陸啦」；再被市民問佢，有人要焦土射落海，佢答：「燒左香港令香港變大陸，同大陸冇分別，咁不如返大陸啦」<br />\n<br />\n然後「線報」改成「叫黃毓民返大陸」、「叫投白票返大陸」，然後「本土派」就信晒土共報再改圖宣傳"},{"pid":"f99c88b832e55a249b9a3167d4487bb9d0c6e7cd","tid":862941,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"「線報」由上海市政協邱達根投資<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180604/20410578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180604%2F20410578&d=jYrhfx%2BEK%2F53d5JphhnXyv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=235c0b8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180604%2F20410578&h=fb35ecc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180604/20410578</a>"},{"pid":"86bea59612051d00a5393fa5a76c9d0c9b13eea8","tid":862941,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5779bcbf50de28b64451add64498f4509cd9e7d8","tid":862941,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2